Helping Veterans Save for Health Care Act of 2015 

Amends the Internal Revenue Code to&#160;provide that a veteran receiving hospital care or medical services for a service-connected disabililty is not disqualified from participating in or contributing to a tax-preferred health savings account.</summary>
